{"image_id": "IT_2011_page_127", "image_size": [1238, 1613], "ocr": [{"text": "55", "bbox": [608.8, 1515.1, 634.2, 1537.6]}, {"text": "the valuation allowance of $0.7 million in 2011 relates primarily to the release of valuation allowances on federal and state capital loss", "bbox": [70.3, 99.0, 1172.7, 121.5]}, {"text": "carryovers.", "bbox": [70.3, 122.2, 171.2, 144.8]}, {"text": "The Company has established a full valuation allowance against domestic realized and unrealized capital losses, as the future", "bbox": [70.3, 161.9, 1173.0, 184.4]}, {"text": "utilization of these losses is uncertain. As of December 31, 2011, the Company had U.S. federal capital loss carryforwards of $0.8", "bbox": [70.3, 185.3, 1172.7, 207.8]}, {"text": "million, all of which will expire in 2012. The Company also had $0.8 million in state and local capital loss carryforwards that expire", "bbox": [70.3, 208.7, 1172.8, 231.2]}, {"text": "over a similar period of time.", "bbox": [70.4, 232.0, 317.7, 254.5]}, {"text": "As of December 31, 2011, the Company had state and local tax net operating loss carryforwards of $139.9 million, of which $5.0", "bbox": [70.4, 271.6, 1172.9, 294.1]}, {"text": "million expire within one to five years, $114.2 million expire within six to fifteen years, and $20.7 million expire within sixteen to", "bbox": [70.4, 295.0, 1172.8, 317.5]}, {"text": "twenty years. In addition, the Company had non-U.S. net operating loss carryforwards of $27.3 million, of which $2.6 million expire", "bbox": [70.4, 318.4, 1172.8, 340.9]}, {"text": "over the next 20 years and $24.7 million that can be carried forward indefinitely. As of December 31, 2011 the Company also had", "bbox": [70.4, 341.7, 1172.8, 364.2]}, {"text": "foreign tax credit carryforwards of $10.0 million, the majority of which expire in 2018.", "bbox": [70.4, 365.1, 789.6, 387.6]}, {"text": "The differences between the U.S. federal statutory income tax rate and the Company’s effective tax rate on income before in