, 587.9, 1158.0, 610.5]}, {"text": "Foreign tax credits ...............................................................................................................................", "bbox": [70.3, 611.3, 892.5, 633.9]}, {"text": "(2.3)", "bbox": [943.0, 611.3, 987.2, 633.9]}, {"text": "(0.8)", "bbox": [1031.0, 611.3, 1075.1, 633.9]}, {"text": "(1.9)", "bbox": [1118.9, 611.3, 1158.0, 633.9]}, {"text": "Record (release) reserve for tax contingencies ....................................................................................", "bbox": [70.3, 634.6, 892.8, 657.2]}, {"text": "3.1", "bbox": [950.1, 634.6, 980.7, 657.2]}, {"text": "2.0", "bbox": [1038.0, 634.6, 1068.5, 657.2]}, {"text": "(3.5)", "bbox": [1119.0, 634.6, 1158.0, 657.2]}, {"text": "Other items, net ....................................................................................................................................", "bbox": [70.3, 658.0, 892.6, 680.6]}, {"text": "(0.6)", "bbox": [943.1, 658.0, 987.3, 680.6]}, {"text": "(0.9)", "bbox": [1031.1, 658.0, 1075.2, 680.6]}, {"text": "1.0", "bbox": [1125.9, 658.0, 1156.3, 680.6]}, {"text": "Effective tax rate ..................................................................................................................................", "bbox": [70.3, 682.4, 892.6, 705.0]}, {"text": "32.3%  28.2%  28.2%", "bbox": [920.4, 682.4, 1168.1, 705.0]}, {"text": "As of December 31, 2011 and December 31 2010, the Company had gross unrecognized tax benefits of $18.3 million and $15.8", "bbox": [70.3, 725.1, 1173.3, 747.6]}, {"text": "million, respectively. The increase is primarily attributable to uncertainties surrounding the utilization of certain tax attributes. It is", "bbox": [70.3, 748.5, 1172.8, 771.0]}, {"text": "reasonably possible that the gross unrecognized tax benefits will be decreased by $2.9 million within the next 12 months due primarily", "bbox": [70.3, 771.8, 1172.7, 794.3]}, {"text": "to anticipated settlements of audits and the expiration of certain statutes of limitation. The benefits in question relate primarily to the", "bbox": [70.3, 795.2, 1172.7, 817.7]}, {"text": "utilization of certain tax attributes.", "bbox": [70.3, 818.6, 361.3, 841.1]}, {"text": "The Company classifies uncertain tax positions not expected to be settled within one year as long term liabilities. As of December 31,", "bbox": [70.3, 858.1, 1172.8, 880.6]}, {"text": "2011 and December 31, 2010, the Company had Other Liabilities of $15.4 million and $15.7 million, respectively, related to long term", "bbox": [70.3, 881.5, 1172.8, 904.0]}, {"text": "uncertain tax positions.", "bbox": [70.3, 904.9, 269.6, 927.4]}, {"text": "The Company records accrued interest and penalties related to unrecognized tax benefits in its income tax provision. As of December", "bbox": [70.3, 944.4, 1172.8, 966.9]}, {"text": "31, 2011 and December 31, 2010, the Company had $4.8 million and $3.8 million of accrued interest and penalties, respectively,", "bbox": [70.3, 967.8, 1173.1, 990.3]}, {"text": "related to unrecognized tax benefits. These amounts are in addition to the gross unrecognized tax benefits noted above. The total", "bbox": [70.3, 991.2, 1172.8, 1013.8]}, {"text": "amount of interest and penalties recognized in the Consolidated Statements of Operations for years ending December 31, 2011 and", "bbox": [70.3, 1014.6, 1172.7, 1037.2]}, {"text": "2010 was $1.5 million and $1.0 million, respectively.", "bbox": [70.3, 1037.9, 514.4, 1060.4]}, {"text": "The following is a reconciliation of the beginning and ending amount of unrecognized tax benefits, excluding interest and penalties,", "bbox": [70.3, 1077.5, 1172.8, 1100.1]}, {"text": "for the years ending December 31 (in thousands):", "bbox": [70.3, 1100.9, 482.8, 1123.5]}, {"text": "2011", "bbox": [983.1, 1143.2, 1046.9, 1165.8]}, {"text": "2010", "bbox": [1092.8, 1143.2, 1156.6, 1165.8]}, {"text": "Beginning balance .................................................................